  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "師古曰：「漢制，三公號稱萬石，其俸月各三百五十斛穀。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "其稱中二千石者月各百八十斛，二千石者百二十斛，比二千石者百斛，千石者九十斛，比千石者八十斛，六百石者七十斛，比六百石者六十斛，四百石者五十斛，比四百石者四十五斛，三百石者四十斛，比三百石者三十七斛，二百石者三十斛，比二百石者二十七斛，一百石者十六斛。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "〉",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "易敘宓羲、神農、黃帝作敎化民，[1]而傳述其官，[2]以為宓羲龍師名官，[3]神農火師火名，[4]黃帝雲師雲名，[5]少昊鳥師鳥名。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "[6]自顓頊以來，為民師而命以民事，[7]有重黎、句芒、祝融、后土、蓐收、玄冥之官，然已上矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "[8]書載唐虞之際，命羲和四子[9]順天文，授民時；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "咨四岳，以舉賢材，揚側陋；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "[10]十有二牧，柔遠能邇；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "[11]禹作司空，平水土；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "[12]棄作后稷，播百穀；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "[13]禼作司徒，敷五敎；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "[14]咎繇作士，正五刑；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "[15]垂作共工，利器用；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "[16]�作朕虞，育草木鳥獸；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "[17]伯夷作秩宗，典三禮；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "[18]夔典樂，和神人；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "[19]龍作納言，出入帝命。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "[20]夏、殷亡聞焉，[21]周官則備矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "[22]天官冢宰，地官司徒，春官宗伯，夏官司馬，秋官司冦，冬官司空，是為六卿，[23]各有徒屬職分，用於百事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "[24]太師、太傅、太保，是為三公，[25]蓋參天子，坐而議政，無不緫統，故不以一職為官名。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "又立三少為之副，少師、少傅、少保，是為孤卿，與六卿為九焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "記曰三公無官，言有其人然后充之，[26]舜之於堯，伊尹於湯，周公、召公於周，是也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "或說司馬主天，司徒主人，司空主土，是為三公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "四岳謂四方諸侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "自周衰，官失而百職亂，戰國並爭，各變異。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "秦兼天下，建皇帝之號，[27]立百官之職。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "漢因循而不革，[28]明簡易，隨時宜也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "其後頗有所改。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "王莽篡位，慕從古官，而吏民弗安，亦多虐政，遂以亂亡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "故略表舉大分，[29]以通古今，備溫故知新之義云。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "[30]",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "太傅，古官，高后元年初置，金印紫綬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "後省，八年復置。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "後省，哀帝元壽二年復置。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "位在三公上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "太師、太保，皆古官，平帝元始元年皆初置，金印紫綬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "太師位在太傅上，太保次太傅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "前後左右將軍，皆周末官，秦因之，位上卿，金印紫綬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "漢不常置，或有前後，或有左右，皆掌兵及四夷。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "有長史，秩千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "廷尉，秦官，[59]掌刑辟，有正、左右監，秩皆千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "景帝中六年更名大理，武帝建元四年復為廷尉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "宣帝地節三年初置左右平，秩皆六百石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "哀帝元壽二年復為大理。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "王莽改曰作士。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "宗正，秦官，[63]掌親屬，有丞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "平帝元始四年更名宗伯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "屬官有都司空令丞，[64]內官長丞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "[65]又諸公主家令、門尉皆屬焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "王莽并其官於秩宗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "初，內官屬少府，中屬主爵，後屬宗正。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "自太常至執金吾，秩皆中二千石，丞皆千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "太子太傅、少傅，古官。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "屬官有太子門大夫、[80]庶子、[81]先馬、[82]舍人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "詹事，秦官，[85]掌皇后、太子家，有丞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "[86]屬官有太子率更、家令丞，僕、中盾、衞率、厨廄長丞，[87]又中長秋、私府、永巷、倉、廄、祠祀、食官令長丞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "諸宦官皆屬焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "[88]成帝鴻嘉三年省詹事官，并屬大長秋。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "[89]長信詹事掌皇太后宮，景帝中六年更名長信少府，[90]平帝元始四年更名長樂少府。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "將行，秦官，[91]景帝中六年更名大長秋，[92]或用中人，或用士人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "[93]",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "水衡都尉，[95]武帝元鼎二年初置，掌上林苑，有五丞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "屬官有上林、均輸、御羞、禁圃、輯濯、鍾官、技巧、六廄、辯銅九官令丞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "[96]又衡官、水司空、都水、農倉，又甘泉上林、都水七官長丞皆屬焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "上林有八丞十二尉，均輸四丞，御羞兩丞，都水三丞，禁圃兩尉，甘泉上林四丞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "成帝建始二年省技巧、六廄官。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "王莽改水衡都尉曰予虞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "初，御羞、上林、衡官及鑄錢皆屬少府。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "自太子太傅至右扶風，皆秩二千石，丞六百石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "司隷校尉，周官，[105]武帝征和四年初置。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "持節，從中都官徒千二百人，[106]捕巫蠱，督大姦猾。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "[107]後罷其兵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "察三輔、三河、弘農。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "元帝初元四年去節。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "成帝元延四年省。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "綏和二年，哀帝復置，但為司隷，冠進賢冠，屬大司空，比司直。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "城門校尉掌京師城門屯兵，有司馬、[108]十二城門候。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "[109]中壘校尉掌北軍壘門內，外掌西域。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "[110]屯騎校尉掌騎士。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "步兵校尉掌上林苑門屯兵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "越騎校尉掌越騎。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "[111]長水校尉掌長水宣曲胡騎。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "[112]又有胡騎校尉，掌池陽胡騎，不常置。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "[113]射聲校尉掌待詔射聲士。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "[114]虎賁校尉掌輕車。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "凡八校尉，皆武帝初置，有丞、司馬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "[115]",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "自司隷至虎賁校尉，秩皆二千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "西域都護加官，宣帝地節二年初置，以騎都尉、諫大夫使護西域三十六國，有副校尉，秩比二千石，丞一人，司馬、候、千人各二人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "戊己校尉，元帝初元元年置，[116]有丞、司馬各一人，候五人，秩比六百石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "奉軍都尉掌御乘輿車，駙馬都尉掌駙馬，[117]皆武帝初置，秩比二千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "侍中、左右曹、諸吏、散騎、中常侍，皆加官，[118]所加或列侯、將軍、卿大夫、將、都尉、尚書、太醫、太官令至郎中，亡員，[119]多至數十人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "侍中、中常侍得入禁中，諸曹受尚書事，諸吏得舉法，散騎騎並乘輿車。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "[120]給事中亦加官，[121]所加或大夫、博士、議郎，掌顧問應對，位次中常侍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "中黃門有給事黃門，位從將大夫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "皆秦制。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "爵：一級曰公士，[122]二上造，[123]三簪裊，[124]四不更，[125]五大夫，[126]六官大夫，七公大夫，[127]八公乘，[128]九五大夫，[129]十左庶長，十一右庶長，[130]十二左更，十三中更，十四右更，[131]十五少上造，十六大上造，[132]十七駟車庶長，[133]十八大庶長，[134]十九關內侯，[135]二十徹侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "[136]皆秦制，以賞功勞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "徹侯金印紫綬，避武帝諱，曰通侯，或曰列侯，改所食國令長名相，又有家丞、門大夫、庶子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "諸侯王，高帝初置，[137]金璽盭綬，[138]掌治其國。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "有太傅輔王，內史治國民，中尉掌武職，丞相統衆官，羣卿大夫都官如漢朝。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "景帝中五年令諸侯王不得復治國，天子為置吏，改丞相曰相，省御史大夫、廷尉、少府、宗正、愽士官，大夫、謁者、郎諸官長丞皆損其員。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "武帝改漢內史為京兆尹，中尉為執金吾，郎中令為光祿勳，故王國如故。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "損其郎中令，秩千石；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "改太僕曰僕，秩亦千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "成帝綏和元年省內史，更令相治民，如郡太守，中尉如郡都尉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "郡守，秦官，掌治其郡，秩二千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "有丞，邊郡又有長史，掌兵馬，秩皆六百石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "景帝中二年更名太守。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "郡尉，秦官，掌佐守典武職甲卒，秩比二千石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "有丞，秩皆六百石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "景帝中二年更名都尉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "關都尉，秦官。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "農都尉、屬國都尉，皆武帝初置。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "縣令、長，皆秦官，掌治其縣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "萬戶以上為令，秩千石至六百石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "減萬戶為長，秩五百石至三百石。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "皆有丞、尉，秩四百石至二百石，是為長吏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "[140]百石以下有斗食、佐史之秩，[141]是為少吏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "大率十里一亭，亭有長。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "十亭一鄉，鄉有三老、有秩、嗇夫、游徼。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "三老掌敎化。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "嗇夫職聽訟，收賦稅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "游徼徼循禁賊盜。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "縣大率方百里，其民稠則減，稀則曠，鄉、亭亦如之，皆秦制也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "列侯所食縣曰國，皇太后、皇后、公主所食曰邑，有蠻夷曰道。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "凡縣、道、國、邑千五百八十七，鄉六千六百二十二，亭二萬九千六百三十五。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0128",
          "zh": "凡吏秩比二千石以上，皆銀印青綬，[142]光祿大夫無。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "Chinese text: This work was published before January 1,",
              "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0129",
          "zh": "[143]秩比六百石以上，皆銅印黑綬，大夫、博士、御史、謁者、郎無。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "1923,",
              "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0130",
          "zh": "[144]其僕射、御史治書尚符璽者，有印綬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "and is in the",
              "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0131",
          "zh": "比二百石以上，皆銅印黃綬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0132",
          "zh": "[145]成帝陽朔二年除八百石、五百石秩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0133",
          "zh": "綏和元年，長、相皆黑綬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0134",
          "zh": "哀帝建平二年，復黃綬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0135",
          "zh": "吏員自佐史至丞相，十三萬二百八十五人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Chinese text: This work was published before January 1, 1923, and is in the",
          "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
